data.description:
5.17 acres nestled in the trees with Private Drive. Private and secluded in Palo Pinto County.  This charm has been completely renovated.  
2432 total sq feet  move in ready.   Two living areas one with a wood burning fireplace.  Huge Kitchen with breakfast bar.  Split bedrooms.  Master Suite has walk in closet and oversized Master Bath with separate vanities and separate shower.  Three Bedrooms and two and half baths.  Also separate study or office off of the master bedroom suite.  Large Breakfast dining area.  Carpet and Vinyl.   If you are tired of the City this is perfect.  Ten minute drive to Mineral Wells.
